00:27:51.650 --> 00:27:54.280 align:middle line:90%


00:27:54.280 --> 00:27:57.910 align:middle line:84%
Let's say you go out in the
sun, and you get too much sun.

00:27:57.910 --> 00:27:59.200 align:middle line:90%
It's real hot.

00:27:59.200 --> 00:28:00.700 align:middle line:90%
Well, that's a stress.

