from the sunlight.

00:28:41.720 --> 00:28:45.460 align:middle line:84%
That's the way our
body adapts to stress.

00:28:45.460 --> 00:28:51.300 align:middle line:84%
Now, not enough sun
is also a stress,

00:28:51.300 --> 00:28:54.020 align:middle line:84%
because your body
needs sunlight.

00:28:54.020 --> 00:28:56.600 align:middle line:90%
It's an essential nutrient.

00:28:56.600 --> 00:28:58.840 align:middle line:84%
It creates essential
nutrients in your body.

00:28:58.840 --> 00:29:00.247 align:middle line:90%
Not enough sun is a stress.

00:29:00.247 --> 00:29:02.830 align:middle line:84%
So if you're in the wintertime,
you're not getting enough sun,

00:29:02.830 --> 00:29:03.955 align:middle line:90%
the exact opposite happens.

00:29:03.955 --> 00:29:06.960 align:middle line:84%
Your skin gets real light
so it can absorb more sun.

00:29:06.960 --> 00:29:09.800 align:middle line:84%
That's how our body
adapts to stresses.

00:29:09.800 --> 00:29:11.250 align:middle line:90%
Too much sun is a stress.

00:29:11.250 --> 00:29:12.985 align:middle line:90%
Not enough sun is a stress.

00:29:12.985 --> 00:29:15.110 align:middle line:84%
So your body's going to
come up with the right skin

00:29:15.110 --> 00:29:17.270 align:middle line:84%
tone for whatever
living environment

00:29:17.270 --> 00:29:20.990 align:middle line:84%
you're in to maximize
the benefits of the sun

00:29:20.990 --> 00:29:24.410 align:middle line:84%
and prevent the harmful
side effects of the sun.

00:29:24.410 --> 00:29:25.940 align:middle line:90%
That's how our bodies adapt.

00:29:25.940 --> 00:29:31.040 align:middle line:10%
And our bodies way
of adapting has

00:29:31.040 --> 00:29:33.830 align:middle line:10%
enabled us to
populate environments

00:29:33.830 --> 00:29:35.360 align:middle line:10%
all over the world.

00:29:35.360 --> 00:29:39.020 align:middle line:84%
And it's the exact
