living environment,

00:36:05.800 --> 00:36:08.240 align:middle line:90%
there were wild tigers.

00:36:08.240 --> 00:36:10.510 align:middle line:84%
And every couple of
weeks, or every couple

00:36:10.510 --> 00:36:15.090 align:middle line:84%
of days, whatever, they
came into your village,

00:36:15.090 --> 00:36:17.010 align:middle line:90%
and they chased you.

00:36:17.010 --> 00:36:20.300 align:middle line:84%
And if you weren't lightning
fast, you were dead.

00:36:20.300 --> 00:36:24.030 align:middle line:90%


00:36:24.030 --> 00:36:25.260 align:middle line:90%
You know, I thought about it.

00:36:25.260 --> 00:36:29.350 align:middle line:84%
I thought, you don't really
need to be faster than a tiger

00:36:29.350 --> 00:36:32.012 align:middle line:90%
to escape being attacked.

00:36:32.012 --> 00:36:34.512 align:middle line:84%
You just need to be faster than
the guy running next to you.

00:36:34.512 --> 00:36:35.660 align:middle line:90%
[LAUGHTER]

00:36:35.660 --> 00:36:37.440 align:middle line:90%
Right?

00:36:37.440 --> 00:36:39.720 align:middle line:90%
Sorry, Bob.

00:36:39.720 --> 00:36:42.420 align:middle line:90%
Always did like you.

00:36:42.420 --> 00:36:44.120 align:middle line:90%
But you have to be fast.

00:36:44.120 --> 00:36:46.320 align:middle line:84%
And if you're not lightning
fast, you're dead.

00:36:46.320 --> 00:36:50.740 align:middle line:84%
That's a different
type of stress

00:36:50.740 --> 00:36:55.140 align:middle line:84%
that causes different
chemistry in your body.

00:36:55.140 --> 00:36:59.280 align:middle line:84%
That chemistry alerts
your body to the fact

00:36:59.280 --> 00:37:03.120 align:middle line:84%
that if you are not
thin, you are dead.

00:37:03.120 --> 00:37:06.510 align:middle line:84%
I call it the the get thin
or get eaten adaptation.

00:37:06.510 --> 00:37:14.488 align:middle line:84%
When that happens, your body
goes, we need to be 60 kilos.

00:37:14.488 --> 00:37:15.780 align:middle line:90%
We need to shed all our weight.

00:37:15.780 --> 00:37:18.210 align:middle line:84%
It makes your body
want to be thinner.

00:37:18.210 --> 00:37:21.120 align:middle line:10%
So a famine is going to make
your body want to be fatter,

00:37:21.120 --> 00:37:23.880 align:middle line:10%
and a tiger is going to make
your body want to be thinner.

00:37:23.880 --> 00:37:24.870 align:middle line:10%
These are programs.

00:37:24.870 --> 00:37:28.260 align:middle line:84%
Survival programs that we
have in our body to help us

00:37:28.260 --> 00:37:29.220 align:middle line:90%
stay alive.

00:37:29.220 --> 00:37:30.300 align:middle line:90%
What's the threat?

00:37:30.300 --> 00:37:31.290 align:middle line:90%
Starving to death?

00:37:31.290 --> 00:37:33.140 align:middle line:90%
Get fatter.

00:37:33.140 --> 00:37:34.810 align:middle line:90%
Slow down your metabolism.

00:37:34.810 --> 00:37:35.810 align:middle line:90%
Be sedentary.

00:37:35.810 --> 00:37:36.860 align:middle line:90%
What's the threat?

00:37:36.860 --> 00:37:38.150 align:middle line:90%
Tigers can eat you?

00:37:38.150 --> 00:37:40.340 align:middle line:90%
Get thinner.

00:37:40.340 --> 00:37:43.607 align:middle line:84%
You develop the
metabolism of a greyhound.

00:37:43.607 --> 00:37:44.690 align:middle line:90%
You just eat a little bit.

00:37:44.690 --> 00:37:45.560 align:middle line:84%
You're like, I'm
not hungry anymore.

00:37:45.560 --> 00:37:47.410 align:middle line:84%
Your brain starts
listening to your stomach.

00:37:47.410 --> 00:37:48.660 align:middle line:90%
You have a little bit of food.

00:37:48.660 --> 00:37:51.080 align:middle line:84%
And if you look at
naturally thin people

00:37:51.080 --> 00:37:55.162 align:middle line:84%
and if you notice when they
eat, they'll eat milkshakes,

00:37:55.162 --> 00:37:56.870 align:middle line:84%
and they'll eat pizza
and something else,

00:37:56.870 --> 00:37:58.537 align:middle line:84%
but they'll just take
a couple of bites,

00:37:58.537 --> 00:38:00.880 align:middle line:90%
and it's sitting there.

00:38:00.880 --> 00:38:02.425 align:middle line:84%
And you're staring
at that pizza.

00:38:02.425 --> 00:38:04.420 align:middle line:90%


