a starvation response.

00:44:23.270 --> 00:44:26.150 align:middle line:90%
Obesity is caused by starvation.

00:44:26.150 --> 00:44:29.500 align:middle line:84%
Number two, if it's
caused by starvation,

00:44:29.500 --> 00:44:33.790 align:middle line:84%
