to cut foods out but to add.

00:44:33.790 --> 00:44:35.880 align:middle line:84%
Add the foods your
body is starving for.

00:44:35.880 --> 00:44:38.680 align:middle line:84%
So the only way you can
be off the Gabriel Method,

00:44:38.680 --> 00:44:40.330 align:middle line:84%
if there's a method,
is if you're not

00:44:40.330 --> 00:44:43.257 align:middle line:84%
adding everyday the
specific nutrients you need.

00:44:43.257 --> 00:44:45.590 align:middle line:84%
You're not going to lose 20
kilos in 20 days doing that,

00:44:45.590 --> 00:44:47.320 align:middle line:84%
