00:44:50.590 --> 00:44:52.660 align:middle line:84%
And you will speed
up your metabolism.

00:44:52.660 --> 00:44:55.030 align:middle line:84%
Your body will
want to be thinner.

00:44:55.030 --> 00:44:59.060 align:middle line:84%
So a nutritional family can
activate the fat programs.

